Install tailscale with admin console

Allow ip forwarding temporarily
sudo sysctl -w net.ipv4.ip_forward=1
sudo sysctl -w net.ipv6.conf.all.forwarding=1

Edit /etc/sysctl.conf and add the following:
net.ipv4.ip_forward = 1
net.ipv6.conf.all.forwarding = 1

Apply changes and restart:
sudo sysctl -p

Bring up tailscale:
sudo tailscale up --advertise-exit-node --advertise-routes=192.168.1.0/24

Approve changes in console
